Author: k_otamatone
Text: I fucking loved that documentary. Literally broke me. I made a post about it soon after it came out you can go read that one if you care

Author: kmrlort
Text: I love Taylor, and it meant a lot to me that she was so open about her ED on her documentary. Not many celebrities (if any that I can think of) would openly admit to an enormous audience that they have disordered eating habits. It kind of broke my heart to hear Taylor say she was still somewhat struggling with accepting her appearance too :(
